tooltips.devices: A live overview of all the devices to help you monitor your lab.

tooltips.parts:

Review print jobs that have been created.

tooltips.templates: Lists all the templates in the Funnel. These control which materials, print settings and printers are used for each part type.
tooltips.timeline: See the print jobs you have queued on each of your devices to monitor progress & utilisation.
